reviews.author: Sergej Baskow
reviews.content:
I recently stumbled upon a little gem of a cannabis dispensary in Koh Phangan and let me tell you, it was a trip. From the moment I walked in, I was greeted by a friendly and knowledgeable staff member who asked me about my preferences and gave me recommendations based on my needs (or what they assumed my needs were based on my hazy expression). The dispensary had a wide selection of top-notch cannabis products, including various strains of flower, edibles, and topicals.

But the real highlight of my visit was the staff. They were absolute experts at making me feel welcome and comfortable, even as I struggled to form coherent sentences. They took the time to explain the different options and answered all of my slurred questions with patience and grace.

In addition to the excellent customer service, the dispensary itself was spotless and had a cozy atmosphere. It was clear that the staff took pride in maintaining the space and ensuring that it was a chill place for customers to shop (or sit and stare at the wall for a while).

Overall, my experience at this cannabis dispensary in Koh Phangan was top-notch. The staff were knowledgeable, friendly, and provided first-class customer service. The selection of products was impressive, and the atmosphere was clean and welcoming. I would highly recommend this dispensary to anyone looking for a top-quality cannabis shopping experience ü´∂
